{
  "id": "adv_main_02_06_01",
  "title": "東京編2章1話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "今のターン、ちょっとタイミング合ってなかったよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our timing was off on that last turn‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "そう？　私は問題ないと思ったけど……\n{user}さん、どうでしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? I thought it was okay.\n{user}-san‚ how was it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（あの電話の主は……姫野さんだった。今まで）\n（何をしていたんだ？　そもそもどうして俺に……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It was Himeno-san who just called me. What has she been up to）\n（all this time? And why did she call me of all people?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、どうかしましたか？\n今の振り付けそんなに変でした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ is something wrong?\nWas our dancing really that strange?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.369771182898322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　ごめん、ちょっと考え事してた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Oh‚ sorry. I just had something on my mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "いいですけど、{user}さんも\nお疲れなら休んで下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s fine‚ {user}-san.\nBut‚ if you’re tired‚ you should take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ\n{user}さんが倒れたりしたら大変なんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s right.\nWe would be in big trouble if you fell ill.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、気をつけるよ\nみんなは心配しないでレッスンに集中してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks. I’ll be careful.\nDon’t worry about me and just focus on your lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3166.6666666666642,
          "startTime": 48
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりやすいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….What an easy guy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "……せやねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….That’s for sure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 56.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "遅くなったけど、これなら約束の時間に間に合うな\nそれにしても、指定した場所がまさか――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m running late‚ but I should still make it to the meeting on time.\nStill‚ I’m surprised that the meeting place is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 65.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "どこなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 66.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "どこなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where is your meeting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 68.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 68.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　君達、帰ったんじゃ……\nどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?! Girls‚ I thought you’d left…\nWhat’s the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたのは、うちらのセリフやんか\n今日は一日中難しい顔して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right back at you.\nYou’ve had a perplexed look on your face all day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 79.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "何か悩んでるんちゃうかなぁって思ってたら\n葵ちゃんが心当たりがあるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you had something troubling you‚\nthen Aoi-chan told me she had a hunch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 85.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "今朝、かかってきた電話が原因だよね？\n相手は誰？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That phone call you got this morning is the reason‚ right?\nWho was it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 89.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "い、いやいや、考え過ぎだよ。俺は夜食を買いに\nただコンビニに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ no‚ you’re just overthinking things. I have to buy myself dinner‚\nso I’m just headed to the convenience store…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 95.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "コンビニ行くのに\nなんできっちりスーツ着てんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re just headed to the convenience store‚\nthen why are you wearing a proper suit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 99.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、{user}さんは\nウソが下手やね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ {user}-san‚\nyou’re a terrible liar.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 103.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "今回の事件のことで、誰かと会うんでしょ？\nそれなら僕達も行く",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re meeting up with someone to discuss the scandal‚ right?\nThen we’re coming with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "うちの予想やと\n姫野さんと密会でもするんちゃいます？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If my intuition is correct‚\nperhaps you’re having a secret meeting with Himeno-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 113.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 113.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "僕達はアメリカから戻ったら即解雇されたんだ\n文句の一つも言わないと収まらないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were fired immediately after we got back from the U.S.\nThe least we deserve is an explanation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 121.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "それやったら、うちの瑠依ちゃんなんか\nめっちゃふさぎ込んでしまったんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For that matter‚ just look at our poor Rui-chan.\nShe’s been terribly down in the dumps.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "朝倉社長のこと、すぐにでも話してもらわんと！\nうちもすみれちゃんもめっちゃ怒ってるんよ",
      "translations": {
